<br />

<br />
That extra money will be a bill to the Demo's if they lose the recount.  I have no idea what happens if they don't cough up the extra once the bill is sent (if the Demo loses... because they get a rebate if the vote result changes in their favor).  Maybe the State will foreclose on the Democrats in WA and sell them off to the highest bidder.  Most likely, cash will flow and they will pay the bill, but I'm drooling over the potential consequences of the Demo's not paying up.  I have no idea what would happen, but I'm sure it will be cool to watch it play out if there is a problem.
<br />

<br />
Ozbee
<br />
...imagining the possibilities.  Desperate Housewives will have nothing on this if it goes to foreclosure.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
